The Stone is prepared in an empty furnace, with a threefold line of
circumvallation, in a tightly closed chamber. It is subjected to continued
coction, till all moisture and clouds are driven off, and the King attains
to indestructible fixedness, and is no longer liable to any danger or injury,
because he has become unconquerable.
